<div class="panel">
<p>Good communication skills. The essence of a trainer's job is to get information across to others in a way that helps them learn. Enthusiasm for learning scratch a trainer, and you'll usually find someone who loves to learn. That's good because trainers are in constant learning mode.</p>
</div>
